{"tid":2213961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院通過法案　限制從新疆進口強迫勞工生產的產品","createTime":"2020-09-23T02:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T14:49:05.000Z","uid":227801,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8783ebdda067d056136f5001e576046d4e88c086","tid":2213961,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"美眾議院通過法案　限制從新疆進口強迫勞工生產的產品<br />\n<br />\n美國國會眾議院以大比數通過《防止強迫維吾爾勞動法》，限制從中國進口強迫勞工生產的產品，受影響的包括新疆在內的中國大部分輸美棉花製品、以及番茄等產品。議案由民主共和兩黨部分議員今年3月聯署提出，眾議院在406票贊成、3票反對、22人棄權之下通過議案，隨後將送到參議院表決，再送交總統特朗普簽署成為法案。美國期望透過議案，就中國對待維吾爾人的方式，向中方加大施壓力度。眾議院議長波洛西早前表示，不應因為商業利益而拒絕就中國的人權發聲。中方一直否認有強迫維吾爾人勞動、以及在新疆興建再教育營的情況。<br />\n<br />\n2020-09-23 10:33:47<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551134-20200923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551134-20200923.htm&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I27TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=b98c6454\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551134-20200923.htm&h=e6896488\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551134-20200923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9f4304dc920452d8756a7102aef228d3d8c2a57a","tid":2213961,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"哩d 血貨一早就唔應該買"},{"pid":"61c617275a0097e5b90fb64722c8a49b3cf33b4e","tid":2213961,"uid":266676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"反支那跟本就2黨共識"},{"pid":"c565c9bb2cf88e4f9bcbb38a48d373d18da0460a","tid":2213961,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb9abec4204d5eee8a602e6e04e99dfcd035a1f","tid":2213961,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T04:22:24.000Z","msg":"拜登見到應該好唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class